'''四碘合汞(II)酸铊(I)'''是一种[[配位化合物|配位化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为Tl<sub>2</sub>[HgI<sub>4</sub>]。它可由[[硝酸亚铊|硝酸亚铊]]和[[碘化汞钾|碘化汞钾]]反应得到。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Raman Spectroscopy|volume=14|issue=3|language=en|date=1983-06|pages=154–161|doi=10.1002/jrs.1250140306|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1002/jrs.1250140306|title=Spectroscopy at very high pressures: 45-structural phase transitions in A2HgI4, (A = Ag, Cu, Tl, 1/2Pb), investigated by Raman scattering|accessdate=2019-05-31|author=David M. Adams, Peter D. Hatton}}</ref>

==物理性质==
四碘合汞(II)酸铊(I)是橙色固体，在116.5℃由橙色变为红色。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Chemical Reviews|volume=68|issue=6|language=en|issn=0009-2665|date=1968-12|pages=649–657|doi=10.1021/cr60256a001|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/cr60256a001|title=Thermochromism of inorganic compounds|accessdate=2019-05-31|author=Jesse H. Day|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205125042/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/cr60256a001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Asmussen R W, Andersen P. The Magnetic Properties of the Thermochromic Compounds. ''Acta Chemica Scandinavica'', 1958, 12(5): 939-944.</ref>

